<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The proximity Vim bonus has been increased to 200%, up from 150%.</li><li>The bonus Vim for harassing enemy Shapers is now 40 and 20 Vim (melee and ranged, respectively) up from 30 and 15.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Now shows the Shaper harassment bonus cooldown as a buff on the buff bar. This will inform players when they will be able to receive their bonus Vim from harassing an enemy shaper, and when the effect is still on cooldown.</li></ul>